title: Xin Qi Bao Long Zhan Che 2 Zhi Ji Jia Zhan Long
synopsis: This is a world where humans and dinosaurs coexist in harmony, and all kinds of small dinosaurs live everywhere. They are naughty and greedy like pets, but they are loyal and friendly to humans. Children are eager to own little dinosaurs and become masters at tame dinosaurs-Dragon Fighter! The protagonist Xinqi is an 8-year-old boy who loves natural creatures and small dinosaurs very much. His dream is to become the strongest dragon fighter. To this end, he has to go to three gyms to participate in the assessment and obtain the red bronze qualification. He and his good partner Tyrannosaurus rex, and good friends Haiyue, Xiaohao and Lola formed a team to go on an adventure together in the mysterious dinosaur forest. Along the way, they encountered all kinds of little dinosaurs. They took the initiative to contact and learn about these little dinosaurs and get along with them in the way they like. But in the forest, there is also a group of hunters who like to use tough methods to catch dinosaurs-hunting teams. They fell in love with the power of Tyrannosaurus rex and wanted to use this power for research. In order to catch the Tyrannosaurus rex, they sent super dinosaurs to deal with Xinqi and them. And Xinqi and his friends also used new powers to evolve their partners into dinosaur warriors to fight against the super dinosaurs of the hunting team. In the process, they also saved many small dinosaurs from the hunting team. These little dinosaurs are also influenced by them and are willing to get close (translated from iqiyi)

synopsis: This play tells the story of a group of children who, in order to protect the peace of the city, and their gyro beasts fight against the villains who use the gyro beasts to do bad things. The protagonist Xinqi has a gyro beast named Tyrannosaurus, and they live a noisy but happy life every day. But one day there was a group of people called the "Alien Beast Corps" who stole energy from the city to strengthen their gyro beasts, and even seized other people's gyro beasts as their own. In order to protect the tranquility of the city and prevent them from harming the top beasts, Xinqi and her friends fight with them through top competition. During this process, they grew up with their top beasts, and the emotions between the pets continued to deepen.  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Xiongmao Boshi
synopsis: In the warm and comfortable community of Panda City, everyday life is full of surprises and unexpected tasks. There are various tasks to be done in the community, such as repairing large vehicles, constructing weird buildings, operating quaint shops, and delivering weird packages. The energetic Dr. Panda can always lend a helping hand. By helping his friends and serving the community, he can find fun in a new career or task every day. Because he is full of curiosity and likes to find fun, Dr. Panda can always turn every new challenge into an adventure for himself and his animal friends. Dr. Panda likes each of his friends because they all have unique skills and small habits. Dr. Panda likes to be at the forefront of the team. He believes in proactiveness more than waiting and watching. However, his strong self-confidence is also a small shortcoming, which makes him unable to foresee possible problems. At first glance, this cute little panda seems to lack the ability to solve problems, because he often counts one step at a time. But with his enterprising spirit and optimistic attitude towards life, no matter how difficult the task is, he can be easily solved. He can always find a new perspective or clever way, because he always has a unique insight into the situation before him. When he asks his animal friends for help, most of them need to step out of their comfort zone to adapt to his childlike way of thinking. But in the end, they are always happy to help, because they know that with Dr. Panda, an ordinary day can become an exciting roller coaster journey!  (translated from qq)

title: Haitun Bang Bang Hao
synopsis: This is a joyous adventure story about protecting natural symbiosis and solving puzzles. In our story, five partners with different personalities are a united whole: strong and keen navigator and captain-Dolphin Ke Lanbo; optimistic, whimsical music lover and power manager-Moray Barry ; Shy and patient mechanical engineer and inventor-Crab Robb; studious and wise science doctor and recorder-Turtle Xiaodi; and the most kind and caring health expert and doctor-Cuttlefish Sweet Cocoa . They formed an adventure squad called "Dolphin Gangbang", driving the "Bangbang Express", a sea, land, and air super train, across five continents and four oceans. In this train, each person has his own super boats with unique shapes and different functions, which can be combined into an infinitely powerful "help superman". Together, they observe the symbiotic relationship in this wonderful world, helping various creatures to survive crises and resolve difficulties. With infinite love for this world, they use their abilities to protect the harmony of nature. When there is a problem in the symbiotic relationship, the Dolphin Gang will always arrive as soon as possible. They carefully explored the causes of the problems and used their cleverness to help the creatures in difficulties. In the process of saving and protecting the symbiotic relationship, the team members also learned how to get along with others and nature better.  (translated from iqiyi)

title: Haitun Bang Bang Hao season2
synopsis: This is a joyous and adventurous story about protecting natural symbiosis and solving puzzles. In our story, five partners with different personalities are a united whole: Strong and keen navigator and captain-Dolphin Ke Lanbo; An optimistic and whimsical music lover and power manager-Conger Barry; Shy and patient mechanical engineer and inventor-Crab Rob; A studious and wise science doctor and recorder-Turtle Xiaodi; And the most kind and caring health expert and doctor-Squid Sweet Cocoa. Captain Ke Lanbo drove the Bangbang Express, which can travel up to the world, sea and land, and four other team members, traveling in a group of ecosystems around the world. Bangbang members have their own personalities and specialties. They face difficulties together and are the best partners. When rescuing the creatures, the five people drove their super boats to form a huge robot-to help the superman, to help the trapped creature. In the new stage of the adventure, Bangbang Express will go to the colorful ecosystems in the world, the ice and snowy Antarctica, the dark and mysterious seabed, and the vibrant coral reefs... where they start various adventures. , Discover the laws that animals get along with nature, and then learn and grow under repeated difficulties. At the end of each adventure, the Dolphin Gang’s partners will return to Gangbang Express to review this classic adventure in the cozy little squid restaurant. Sweet cocoa will bring you the most delicious dessert. This is a warm reward time for every adventure, so that every partner loves this team more.  (translated from qq)
